PortSystem 1.0

name			sand
version			0.1.1
revision		1
categories		textproc
platforms		darwin
maintainers		mww@opendarwin.org
description		sand is a tool to help you keep your diary
long_description	${description}

homepage		http://sand.sourceforge.net/
